\p 
\v 1 Tol lan…ôha, nati …ôpnap…®n it…ômah n…ôt…ômimi nak, n…ôm…ô n…ôkotakil mot…ôl…ôhu n…ôghati…ôn r…ôha suah k…ôti o noli…ôn t…ôrah k…ôti r…ôhan,\f + \fr 2:1 \ft N…ôt…ôm Isrel k…ômot…ôni m…ôm…ô Nanihlu…ô m…®n, ilah r…ôfin n…ôt…ôm kot…ôrah m…ôt…ôu-inu Nanihlu…ô m…®n k…ôsotosi…ôn Lou r…ôha Mos…®s.\f* m…ôt…ôu n…ôkotakil mot…ôl…ôhu aru n…ôghati…ôn r…ôhat…ômah. K…ôni r…ôhat…ômah n…ôghati…ôn t…®k…ô o nuhalp…®ni…ôn, m…ôt…ôu it…ômah n…ôt…ôm nautol lan…ôha, nautol noli…ôn t…ôrah m…®n t…ôhmen-…ôhmen …ôm…ô e lah.\x - \xo 2:1 \xt Mat 7:1-2; Jon 8:7\x*\f + \fr 2:1 \ft Fes m…®n u e 2:1‚Äì3:8, Pol t…ôt…ôghati …ôhruahru k…ôm n…ôt…ôm Isrel. T…ôt…ôghati e noli…ôn r…ôhalah i…ôt…ôm n…®kilah t…ôhti m…ôm…ô kot…ôhruahru e n…ôhmt…® Uhg…®n m…ôt…ôu-inu ilah n…ôt…ôm Isrel, k…ôni k…ôutoht…ôu=p…ôn Lou r…ôha Mos…®s. K…ôni n…ôt…ôl…®gi…ôn r…ôhalah m…ôm…ô inu …ôm…ô t…ôhmen m…ôm…ô tatol ilah kot…ôhruahru.\f*
\v 2 K…ôni kitah kot…ôhrun m…ôm…ô nian Uhg…®n t…ôtakil m…ôt…ôl…ôhu n…ôghati…ôn k…ôm n…ôt…ômimi n…ôt…ôm kautol noli…ôn m…®n …ôha i…ôt…ôm i…ôm…ôni r…ôk…®s u, r…ôhan n…ôghati…ôn in t…ôhruahru …ôm…ô.
