\v 3 Tol lan…ôha, nian it…ômah n…ôutakil m…ôut…ôl…ôhu n…ôghati…ôn r…ôha n…ôt…ômimi o n…ôrahi…ôn r…ôhalah, m…ôt…ôu it…ômah nautol noli…ôn …ôhmen-…ôhmen …ôm…ô, k…ôni n…ôkot…ôkeikei mot…ôhrun m…ôm…ô ko n…ôsotag…®mi…ôn nian otakil m…ôl…ôhu n…ôghati…ôn r…ôhat…ômah.
